    <date day="20" month="July" year="2026"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>SMTP [RFC5321] uses opportunistic TLS to optionally protect transport
   sessions.  Secure SMTP uses mandatory TLS on all connections.  It
   also provides a method for SMTP clients to locate Secure SMTP
   servers.</t>
    </abstract>
  </front>
